data.description:
BRICK HOME THAT IS NOT LIKE YOUR TYPICAL WEST END HOUSE. SITS ON .68 ACRES IN TOTAL WITH 5 LOTS. Grand foyer with french doors opens to formal living room with fireplace and built in shelving. office space on main level. Large 4 season sun room.  All bedrooms are upstairs. Huge master bedroom with master closet that will blow you away.Other 2 bedrooms are also large. Huge yard with abundance  of shade and brick garage.  Roof 2011, a/c 08, water heater 2020, furnace 01 
MELISSA WORKS PART TIME AT HOME.  MUST HAVE APPOINTMENT. fridge in sun room does not stay

SALE IS SUBJECT TO OWNERS FINDING A HOME OF THEIR CHOICE.
